@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber

box "Backend System (Sistema AIT)" #LightBlue
    participant "HTTP Request" as HttpRequest
    participant "Route" as Route
    participant "Controller" as Controller
    participant "Dto" as Dto
    participant "Service" as Service
    box "Persistence" #LightGreen
        participant "Data Model" as DataModel
        participant "Aggregate" as Aggregate
        participant "Value Object" as ValueObject
        participant "Entity" as Entity
    end box
    participant "Repository" as Repository
end box

HttpRequest -> Route : 1.1: POST /api/qualifications
activate HttpRequest
Route -> Controller : 1.2: Invoke CreateQualification
activate Route
Controller -> Dto : 1.3: Map request body (CreateQualificationDto)
activate Controller
Dto --> Controller : 1.4: Mapped data
deactivate Dto
Controller -> Service : 1.5: CreateAsync(dto)
activate Service
Service -> Aggregate : 1.6: Create aggregate (new Qualification)
activate Aggregate
Aggregate -> ValueObject : 1.6.1: Create value objects (CodeVO, NameVO, DescVO)
activate ValueObject
ValueObject --> Aggregate : 1.6.2: Value objects created
deactivate ValueObject
Aggregate -> Entity : 1.6.3: Create entity instance
activate Entity
Entity --> Aggregate : 1.6.4: Entity created
deactivate Entity
Aggregate --> Service : 1.6.5: Aggregate created (qualification instance)
deactivate Aggregate
Service -> Repository : 1.7: AddAsync(qualification)
activate Repository
Repository -> DataModel : 1.7.1: Map aggregate to data model (EF Add)
activate DataModel
DataModel --> Repository : 1.7.2: Data model mapped/tracked
deactivate DataModel
Repository --> Service : 1.8: Data persisted/tracked
deactivate Repository
Service -> DataModel : 1.8.1 : SaveChangesAsync()
activate DataModel
DataModel --> Service : 1.8.2 : Changes Saved
deactivate DataModel
Service -> Controller : 1.9: Response data (QualificationDto mapped)
deactivate Service
Controller --> HttpRequest : 1.10: HTTP 201 Created
deactivate Controller
deactivate Route
HttpRequest --> : 1.11: HTTP Response
deactivate HttpRequest

@enduml